<title>Term Project</title>
<h1>Term Project</h1>
<h3>
The goal of the project is to design and develop
a social networking service center.
<br><br>
The social networking service center provides the following capabilities:
<li>Authenticate the user is a registered user 
<li>Let the user select a function
<li>process the function
<li>Enter the results into user records
<li>Provide a learning mode so that a user can try
to learn how to use the social networking service.
<p>
For example, a social networking service for
wedding planning may offer service functions such as:
(a) find a place for wedding ceremony,
(b) find a caterer,
(c) find taxedo rental service for men,
(d) find wedding gown rental service for women,
(e) chat place for newly weds.
<p>
You may use Kinect device as a gestural interface for
the social network defined by your group.  For example
the wedding planner may wave her hands, and a different
wedding gown will appear on the screen!

<br>
